    "content": "-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n                                      Poison - Bell Biv DeVoe\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\nTabbed by: TandyJake\r\n\r\nI know there's not a whole lot to this song, but the bass is kind of catchy and fun to \r\nplay.  It's very simple and there's only two different licks played during the verse and chorus.\r\n\r\nThe bass doesn't come in until they actually start singing.\r\n\r\n\r\n[tab]Intro/Verse\r\n---------------------|---------------------|\r\n---------------------|---------------------|\r\n---------------------|---------------------|\r\n--2----2-4-5-4-5-4---|--2-0-2-4-5-4-5-4----|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[tab]Chorus\r\n----------------------------------------------------|\r\n--------6-7-8---9-8---------------------------------|\r\n--------------------9---------9-11-99-11-9/11-------|\r\n--7----------------------9----------------------7---|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nHope this helps and Enjoy!",
